summary: A player home in Whiterun full of storage tailored for the OCD.
descriptionHtml:
A player home in Whiterun, with 18 custom storage chests and all smithing and enchanting amenities included. 

The home also contains a letter from the previous owner, and is Navmeshed

18 Custom Storage containers include-
- Potions/Poisons
- Weapons/Armor
- Soul Gems
- Scrolls/Spell tomes
- Jewelry/Gems
- Smithing materials
- Cooking ingredients
- Cooked/Raw food
- Alcohol
- Treasures/Common items
author: Rimrald
